annotation.text: 3 CDs in a fatbox with an insert giving tracklists, composers, and times. The discs are unlabeled except for their catalog numbers (5-301-2/1 etc.). The fatbox is in a slipcover mostly reproducing the front and back covers. The fatbox spine just says ''Anthology''; the insert, the fatbox cover, and the slipcase cover all have the (misspelled) title ''The Millenium Anthology''.
